{
  "name": "Apollo-to-Brevo CRM Sync",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "### Apollo-to-Brevo CRM Sync Pipeline\n\n**Required Credentials**:\n- `APOLLO_WEBHOOK_SECRET`: Secret to verify Apollo webhook signature.\n- `APOLLO_API_KEY`: Key for Mixed People Search.\n- `BREVO_API_KEY`: Token for contact updates, list syncs, and lookup queries.\n\n**Environment Variables**:\n- `APOLLO_WEBHOOK_SECRET` mapped in your n8n environment.\n- `APOLLO_API_KEY` mapped in your n8n environment.\n- `BREVO_API_KEY` mapped in your n8n environment.\n- `BREVO_LIST_ID` mapped in your n8n environment.\n- `BREVO_SEQUENCE_TIER_1` and `BREVO_SEQUENCE_TIER_2` mapped in your n8n environment.\n\n**Testing Protocol**:\n1. Test Circular Sync Guard: Send webhook with `AUTOMATION_ORIGIN = n8n_pipeline` and verify the flow aborts immediately.\n2. Verify HMAC Signature Validation: Send a POST with headers and body, checking that signature checks work.\n3. Validate Deduplication lookup in Brevo. Verify 404 routes to Create and 200 routes to Update.\n4. Check Sparse Update Merger: Verify it does not overwrite existing Brevo properties with empty values from Apollo.\n5. Confirm ICP routing logic: Tier 1 goes to personalized sequence, Tier 2 to standard nurture.\n\n**Upsell Note**:\nWant custom CRM fields synced or additional routing steps? Hire **Automation & RevOps by Alfaz**: [whoisalfaz.me/contact/](https://whoisalfaz.me/contact/).",
        "height": 260,
        "width": 640
      },
      "id": "sticky-note-4",
      "name": "Workflow Instructions",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.sticky",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        100,
        -250
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "httpMethod": "POST",
        "path": "apollo-leads-webhook",
        "responseMode": "onReceived",
        "responseData": "allEntries"
      },
      "id": "apollo-webhook",
      "name": "Apollo Webhook Ingest",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.webhook",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        100,
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "conditions": {
          "options": {
            "caseSensitive": true,
            "leftValue": "",
            "typeValidation": "strict"
          },
          "conditions": [
            {
              "id": "cond-syncguard",
              "leftValue": "={{ $json.body?.contact?.attributes?.AUTOMATION_ORIGIN }}",
              "comparison": "notEquals",
              "rightValue": "n8n_pipeline"
            }
          ],
          "combinator": "and"
        }
      },
      "id": "circular-sync-guard",
      "name": "Circular Sync Guard",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.if",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [
        350,
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const crypto = require('crypto');\nconst secret = process.env.APOLLO_WEBHOOK_SECRET || 'YOUR_API_KEY_HERE';\nconst signature = $input.item.json.headers['x-apollo-signature'];\nconst body = JSON.stringify($input.item.json.body);\n\nif (!signature) {\n  throw new Error('Missing x-apollo-signature header.');\n}\n\nconst expected = crypto\n  .createHmac('sha256', secret)\n  .update(body)\n  .digest('hex');\n\nif (signature !== `sha256=${expected}`) {\n  return [{\n    json: {\n      status: \"unauthorized\",\n      message: \"Invalid signature\"\n    }\n  }];\n}\n\nreturn [{\n  json: {\n    status: \"authorized\",\n    data: $input.item.json.body\n  }\n}];"
      },
      "id": "verify-signature",
      "name": "Verify Webhook Signature",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [
        600,
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "conditions": {
          "options": {
            "caseSensitive": true,
            "leftValue": "",
            "typeValidation": "strict"
          },
          "conditions": [
            {
              "id": "cond-signature",
              "leftValue": "={{ $json.status }}",
              "comparison": "equals",
              "rightValue": "authorized"
            }
          ],
          "combinator": "and"
        }
      },
      "id": "is-signature-valid",
      "name": "Is Signature Valid?",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.if",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [
        850,
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "method": "GET",
        "url": "=https://api.brevo.com/v3/contacts/{{ encodeURIComponent($json.data.email || 'test@example.com') }}",
        "sendHeaders": true,
        "headersUi": {
          "parameter": [
            {
              "name": "api-key",
              "value": "={{ process.env.BREVO_API_KEY || 'YOUR_API_KEY_HERE' }}"
            },
            {
              "name": "Accept",
              "value": "application/json"
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      "id": "brevo-lookup",
      "name": "Brevo Lookup",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4,
      "position": [
        1100,
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "conditions": {
          "options": {
            "caseSensitive": true,
            "leftValue": "",
            "typeValidation": "strict"
          },
          "conditions": [
            {
              "id": "cond-lookup",
              "leftValue": "={{ $json.statusCode }}",
              "comparison": "equals",
              "rightValue": 404
            }
          ],
          "combinator": "and"
        }
      },
      "id": "contact-found",
      "name": "Contact Found?",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.if",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [
        1350,
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "method": "POST",
        "url": "https://api.brevo.com/v3/contacts",
        "sendHeaders": true,
        "headersUi": {
          "parameter": [
            {
              "name": "api-key",
              "value": "={{ process.env.BREVO_API_KEY || 'YOUR_API_KEY_HERE' }}"
            },
            {
              "name": "Content-Type",
              "value": "application/json"
            }
          ]
        },
        "sendBody": true,
        "bodyParametersUi": {
          "parameter": [
            {
              "name": "email",
              "value": "={{ $node[\"Is Signature Valid\"].json.data.email }}"
            },
            {
              "name": "attributes",
              "value": "={\n    \"FIRSTNAME\": \"{{ $node[\"Is Signature Valid\"].json.data.first_name }}\",\n    \"LASTNAME\": \"{{ $node[\"Is Signature Valid\"].json.data.last_name }}\",\n    \"COMPANY\": \"{{ $node[\"Is Signature Valid\"].json.data.organization?.name }}\",\n    \"JOBTITLE\": \"{{ $node[\"Is Signature Valid\"].json.data.title }}\",\n    \"LINKEDIN\": \"{{ $node[\"Is Signature Valid\"].json.data.linkedin_url }}\",\n    \"INDUSTRY\": \"{{ $node[\"Is Signature Valid\"].json.data.organization?.industry }}\",\n    \"HEADCOUNT\": \"{{ $node[\"Is Signature Valid\"].json.data.organization?.estimated_num_employees }}\",\n    \"APOLLO_ID\": \"{{ $node[\"Is Signature Valid\"].json.data.id }}\",\n    \"LEAD_SOURCE\": \"apollo_outbound\",\n    \"AUTOMATION_ORIGIN\": \"n8n_pipeline\"\n  }"
            },
            {
              "name": "listIds",
              "value": "=[{{ process.env.BREVO_LIST_ID || 42 }}]"
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      "id": "brevo-create",
      "name": "Brevo Create Contact",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4,
      "position": [
        1600,
        -100
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const existingContact = $node[\"Brevo Lookup\"].json;\nconst apolloData = $node[\"Is Signature Valid\"].json.data;\n\nconst updates = {};\n\nif (!existingContact.attributes?.COMPANY && apolloData.organization?.name) {\n  updates.COMPANY = apolloData.organization.name;\n}\nif (!existingContact.attributes?.JOBTITLE && apolloData.title) {\n  updates.JOBTITLE = apolloData.title;\n}\nif (!existingContact.attributes?.LINKEDIN && apolloData.linkedin_url) {\n  updates.LINKEDIN = apolloData.linkedin_url;\n}\n\nreturn {\n  json: {\n    email: existingContact.email || apolloData.email,\n    attributes: updates,\n    updateEnabled: true\n  }\n};"
      },
      "id": "sparse-update-merger",
      "name": "Sparse Update Merger",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [
        1600,
        100
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "method": "PUT",
        "url": "=https://api.brevo.com/v3/contacts/{{ encodeURIComponent($json.email) }}",
        "sendHeaders": true,
        "headersUi": {
          "parameter": [
            {
              "name": "api-key",
              "value": "={{ process.env.BREVO_API_KEY || 'YOUR_API_KEY_HERE' }}"
            },
            {
              "name": "Content-Type",
              "value": "application/json"
            }
          ]
        },
